data.title: Designated Newspapers For Proof of Publication
data.text:
The following papers are the designated newspapers for proof of publication in Monroe County, New York:

Rochester Business Journal

585-232-6920 (press 3 then 2) or send your notice to [email protected]

Daily Record

585-232-6920 or send your notice to [email protected]

Jewish Ledger

585-427-2468

Mendon-Honeoye Falls-Lima Sentinel

1-844-624-6435 of email [email protected]

Democrat and Chronicle

[email protected]

Webster Herald

585-671-1533

Under New York State law, certain legal actions, most commonly the formation of a limited liability company (LLC) or the application for some liquor licenses, must be published in official newspapers that are designated as such by the clerk of the county in which the action is being taken.
